videos.description: Kentucky's Lynn Bowden Jr. throws a punch at Virginia Tech defensive lineman DaShawn Crawford and then shoves a Wildcats assistant during a pregame scuffle.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Punch thrown in pregame scuffle at Belk Bowl) 2019/12/31 ESHEET

videos.headline: Punch thrown in pregame scuffle at Belk Bowl

videos.description: Lynn Bowden Jr. finds an opening and takes the ball 25 yards to the end zone himself for a Kentucky touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Bowden calls his own number for 25-yard Kentucky TD) 2019/12/31

videos.headline: Bowden calls his own number for 25-yard Kentucky TD

videos.description: Hendon Hooker finds Damon Hazelton for an 18-yard Virginia Tech touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Hooker, Hazelton link up for Hokies' TD) 2019/12/31

videos.headline: Hooker, Hazelton link up for Hokies' TD

videos.description: Hendon Hooker throws through a tight window and connects with Dalton Keene for a 6-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Keene hangs on for 6-yard TD catch) 2019/12/31

videos.headline: Keene hangs on for 6-yard TD catch

videos.description: Christopher Rodriguez Jr. pushes through defenders for a 2-yard Kentucky touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Rodriguez runs in for short Kentucky TD) 2019/12/31

videos.headline: Rodriguez runs in for short Kentucky TD

videos.description: Virginia Tech's Deshawn McClease runs untouched into the end zone with a 43-yard touchdown, giving the Hokies the lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (McClease puts Virginia Tech on top with 43-yard TD) 2019/12/31

videos.headline: McClease puts Virginia Tech on top with 43-yard TD

videos.description: Lynn Bowden Jr. picks up his second rushing touchdown of the day with a 61-yard scramble to tie the game for Kentucky.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Bowden goes practically untouched for 61-yard TD) 2019/12/31

videos.headline: Bowden goes practically untouched for 61-yard TD

videos.description: Lynn Bowden Jr. connects with Josh Ali for a 13-yard game-winning touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Bowden finds Ali to put Kentucky on top with 15 seconds left) 2019/12/31

videos.headline: Bowden finds Ali to put UK on top with 15 seconds left

videos.description: After Virginia Tech attempts a lateral, the ball is fumbled and recovered by Kent Jordan Wright, who returns it 28 yards for a Kentucky touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Kentucky turns Virginia Tech's last play attempt into touchdown) 2019/12/31

videos.headline: Kentucky turns Virginia Tech's last play attempt into touchdown
